<div id="title" class="title-page">
  <div class="title-line-top"></div>
  <p class="title-eyebrow">Complete Edition · Seven Documents</p>
  <h1 class="title-main">The Emanatory Schema</h1>
  <p class="title-sub">A formal metaphysics of archetypal closure, axial transcendence, and cosmological ethics — with applied spiral journal</p>
  <div class="title-ops">
    <span class="title-op">M · Monad</span>
    <span class="title-op">C₁₂ · Field</span>
    <span class="title-op">T · Recursion</span>
    <span class="title-op">S · Spiral</span>
    <span class="title-op">A · Axis</span>
    <span class="title-op">E · Expression</span>
  </div>
  <div class="title-rule"></div>
  <div class="title-nav-grid">
    <a href="#essay" class="title-nav-item"><span class="tni-num">Preface</span><span class="tni-title">The Source-Fire: A Generative Essay</span></a>
    <a href="#analysis" class="title-nav-item"><span class="tni-num">Critical</span><span class="tni-title">Formal Analysis & Paradox Tests</span></a>
    <a href="#book1" class="title-nav-item"><span class="tni-num">Book I</span><span class="tni-title">Archetypal Closure & Axial Transcendence</span></a>
