  <div class="section-head-inner">Daily Micro-Checklist</div>
  <div class="checklist">
    <div class="check-item"><span class="check-box"></span><span><strong>Ground (M):</strong> 2–5 minutes of simple being, no roles.</span></div>
    <div class="check-item"><span class="check-box"></span><span><strong>Body / Structure (Taurus / Capricorn):</strong> one concrete act of care or order.</span></div>
    <div class="check-item"><span class="check-box"></span><span><strong>Shadow glance (Scorpio):</strong> one uncomfortable truth named.</span></div>
    <div class="check-item"><span class="check-box"></span><span><strong>Compassion (Pisces / Libra):</strong> one act of mercy or fairness.</span></div>
    <div class="check-item"><span class="check-box"></span><span><strong>Spiral move (any sign):</strong> one 1% behavior shift toward integration.</span></div>
    <div class="check-item"><span class="check-box"></span><span><strong>Axial pause (A):</strong> 30–60 seconds sensing vertical or inward openness.</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-head-inner">T – S – A Reflection</div>
  <div class="reflection-block">
    <div class="reflect-item"><div class="reflect-q"><span class="reflect-sym">T · Recursion</span><span>What repeated today?</span></div><span class="write-line-long"></span><span class="write-line-long"></span></div>
    <div class="reflect-item"><div class="reflect-q"><span class="reflect-sym">S · Spiral</span><span>Did I respond any differently this time?</span></div><span class="write-line-long"></span><span class="write-line-long"></span></div>
    <div class="reflect-item"><div class="reflect-q"><span class="reflect-sym">A · Axis</span><span>Did anything hint at a larger, vertical perspective?</span></div><span class="write-line-long"></span><span class="write-line-long"></span></div>
  </div>
