  <!-- Weekly Workbook -->

  <div class="book-section">
    <div class="section-head"><span class="sec-roman">§ III</span><h2>12-Week Spiral Workbook — Weekly Page</h2></div>
    <div class="workbook">
      <div class="wb-header"><span class="wb-title">Weekly Spiral Page</span><span class="wb-meta">One sign · One week · One integration</span></div>
      <div class="wb-fields">
        <div class="wb-field"><span class="wb-field-label">Week #</span><span class="wb-line"></span></div>
        <div class="wb-field"><span class="wb-field-label">Sign / Sector</span><span class="wb-line"></span></div>
        <div class="wb-field"><span class="wb-field-label">Dates</span><span class="wb-line"></span></div>
        <div class="wb-field"><span class="wb-field-label">Virtue Focus</span><span class="wb-line"></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="wb-part"><div class="wb-part-title">Part 1 · Opening</div><div class="wb-prompt"><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">Current pattern in this sign — loops, struggles, recurring themes:</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">Concrete intention for this week:</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div></div></div>
      <div class="wb-part"><div class="wb-part-title">Part 2 · Mid-Week Notes (Days 2–5)</div><div class="wb-prompt"><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">How this sign's energy showed up in real life:</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">Virtue moments — wins:</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">Vices noticed (excess / defect):</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">One small adjustment I can try tomorrow:</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div></div></div>
      <div class="wb-part"><div class="wb-part-title">Part 3 · Shadow &amp; Recursion (Day 6)</div><div class="wb-prompt"><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">Recurring loop in this sign — describe:</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">What might this loop be trying to teach me?</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">If I treated this as curriculum instead of fate, what would I do differently?</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div></div></div>
      <div class="wb-part"><div class="wb-part-title">Part 4 · Integration &amp; Axial Alignment (Day 7)</div><div class="wb-prompt"><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">What actually shifted this week?</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">How did this sign help my spiral (S) rather than just my repetition (T)?</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">How might this sign serve my axial orientation (A) going forward?</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span></div><div class="wb-prompt-item"><span class="wb-prompt-q">One sentence intention as I move to the next sign:</span><span class="wb-line-sm"></span><span class="wb-line-lg"></span></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

